	<tr style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
		<td style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"></td>
		<td class="container" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="margin: 0 auto!important;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;display: block!important;max-width: 600px!important;clear: both!important;">

			<div class="content" style="margin: 0 auto;padding: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;max-width: 600px;display: block;">
			<table style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;width: 100%;">
				<tr style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
					<td style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
						<h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeue-Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;line-height: 1.1;margin-bottom: 15px;color: #000;font-weight: 500;font-size: 27px;">Ahoy! <%= @username %></h3>
						<p class="lead" style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.6;">Welcome to Anchorage.io. Here's a couple important things you should know before getting started.</p>

						<!-- Callout Panel -->
						<p class="callout" style="margin: 0;padding: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 15px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.6;background-color: #ECF8FF;">
							Your Email: <strong style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @user.email %></strong><br style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
							Visit Dashboard: <a href="https://anchorage.io/dashboard" style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: #2BA6CB;font-weight: bold;">Dashboard</a>
						</p><!-- /Callout Panel -->

						<p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.6;">To get you started, we gave you a crappy username of <strong style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @username %></strong>. It is highly recommended that you <strong style="color: red;margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">update this username</strong>, along with your profile details. Feel free to add your boat details, backlink your blog, and write a quick bio. It's optional, but you'll earn a few badges for doing so.</p>
						<h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeue-Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;line-height: 1.1;margin-bottom: 15px;color: #000;font-weight: 500;font-size: 27px;">Start Building your Cruising Guide</h3>

						<p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.6;">Anchorage.io allows you to create a custom cruising guide for boating destinations around the world. When you find a location you like, just click the <strong style="color: #aad450;margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Add to Cruising Guide</strong> button.</p>

						<h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;HelveticaNeue-Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;line-height: 1.1;margin-bottom: 15px;color: #000;font-weight: 500;font-size: 27px;">Our Mission</h3>

						<p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.6;">Anchorage.io is a <strong style="color: #4d9de0;margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">free, open-source, community-driven</strong> cruising guide for boaters. Our mission is to create an engaging environment where boaters can share knowledge about the world's finest cruising locations.</p>



					<%= render "social_contact" %>

					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			</div><!-- /content -->

		</td>
		<td style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"></td>
